            <title>2.0.0</title>
            <pubDate>Thu, 30 Apr 2026 11:28:08 -0500</pubDate>
            <sparkle:version>20260430</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>2.0.0</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <description><![CDATA[
                <h2>What's New</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li>Important! New features will only work with recordings made after this update, previous recordings will still work but will be missing the additional features.</li>
                    <li>Enhanced Dashboard</li>
                    <li>Improved Recordings Management and Sorting</li>
                    <li>Improved Timeline</li>
                    <li>NEW! Tags and Notes</li>
                    <li>NEW! Theater Mode</li>
                    <li>NEW! Clips Manager</li>
                    <li>NEW! Create play montages straight from the app by selecting the new montage mode in the clip creator</li>
                    <li>Additional storage management settings</li>
                    <li>Bugfix: Black frames on tab out replaced with gray screen explaining game window is not visible to prevent YouTube from auto trimming empty frames and thus desyncing the audio in uploads.</li>
                    <li>For the full detailed changelog please visit <a href="https://fireflymac.gg/changelog.html">https://fireflymac.gg/changelog.html</a>
                </ul>
            ]]>
            </description>
